nodes.text: Star Wars Weekly 103 is the one hundred third issue of the  Marvel Star Wars UK series of comic books.
This issue reprints the last of four parts of the story printed in the US as Star Wars Annual 1.

The comic also includes the third part of a brand-new section called Star Profile featuring Alec Guinness alongside a study-interview of his career until 1980 including the soon to-be-released Star Wars: Episode V The Empire Strikes Back.
